ing the rigidity\nconditions for ranks $m >> n$. We also prove automatic regularity and rigidity\nestimates for first and higher order derivatives of $\\mathrm{K}$-biinvariant\nmultipliers in the rank 1 groups $SO(n,1)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 18:50:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 May 2019 19:57:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2021 18:35:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-03"}
