". We present our catalogue of\ndetected sources and investigate how our observations compare to previous radio\nobservations. This includes investigating the flux scale calibration of these\nobservations compared to previous measurements, the implied spectral indices of\nthe sources, the observed source counts and corrections to obtain the true\nsource counts, and finally the clustering of the observed radio sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 19:26:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-27"}
