hicknesses have also been\ndemonstrated. The capacitors are then exploited in two fully printed\ndemonstrators: a resistor-capacitor (RC) low-pass filter and a graphene-based\nfield effect transistor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2018 14:34:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-17"}
